---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-zen/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Zen Ledger Advisory | Precision in Silence"
  description="Zen Ledger Advisory brings Japanese minimalist calm and precision to tax, audit, and advisory services."
  active="home"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-zen"
>
<main class="pt-32">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop mb-section-gap">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-end">
<div class="md:col-span-7 pb-unit">
<h1 class="font-zl-display text-zl-display mb-6">Precision in Silence.</h1>
<p class="font-zl-body-lg text-zl-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-md">
                        Navigating complexity through the lens of minimalist financial mastery. We resolve the intricate into the essential.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-5 aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden custom-border">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A high-contrast black and white photograph of a Zen rock garden, focusing on the meticulously raked sand patterns that create sharp, rhythmic shadows. The composition is minimalist and balanced, featuring a single dark stone at the golden ratio point. The lighting is soft yet directional, highlighting the texture of the sand in a pristine light-mode environment. The overall mood is one of profound stillness, order, and quiet luxury." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDI9MqUf-o8kz445oyOthzQIrvym4hURCZtmfoiuJj7rYFHlhuisz0uTAGM-fdBZT3LINRB_yhwe0y-dYKpAbfgGTpB4sd8q7fER6XCvfA_TiHKF-hd3SBggOg-4MrLHojeTvqfEX1iLnhlxkXWsnd3g5uxuk8htmlRdp3fsWrp0r2p5ZpalwiI9OYloduTIUdzD2qgxxbzs_pq2SpkxOkhKUM-ccgXD3eTnSWO-RLcX4QXmU135DxTEDmgdxDa7OuwbNXHHX5EKkAC"/>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Value Proposition / Bento-ish Minimalist Grid -->
<section class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop mb-section-gap">
<div class="horizontal-line mb-12"></div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
<div>
<span class="font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block">Philosophy</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-headline-lg text-zl-headline-lg mb-4">The Clarity of Ma</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        In Japanese aesthetics, 'Ma' is the space between. We apply this to accounting by identifying the signal within the noise, ensuring your financial structure remains lean and purposeful.
                    </p>
</div>
<div>
<span class="font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block">Methodology</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-headline-lg text-zl-headline-lg mb-4">Unerring Accuracy</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        Our advisory isn't just about numbers; it's about the narrative they form. We provide meticulous oversight that allows you to focus on the high-level vision of your enterprise.
                    </p>
</div>
<div>
<span class="font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block">Outcome</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-headline-lg text-zl-headline-lg mb-4">Strategic Quietude</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        The ultimate luxury in finance is the absence of worry. We cultivate a environment of certainty, where every transaction and ledger entry is a step toward enduring stability.
                    </p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Vertical High-Contrast Feature -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-gap">
<div class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between mb-16">
<h2 class="font-zl-display text-zl-headline-lg text-primary max-w-sm">Core Verticals</h2>
<div class="zen-divider hidden md:block"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 border-t border-b border-outline-variant">
<!-- Tax -->
<div class="p-12 md:border-r border-outline-variant hover:bg-background transition-colors duration-500 group">
<div class="mb-12">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">architecture</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-zl-headline-lg text-zl-headline-lg mb-6">Tax</h4>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
                            Sophisticated tax structuring designed for global citizens and complex holdings. Efficiency through structural elegance.
                        </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-zen/services/tax-strategy">
                            Explore Integrity <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_right_alt</span>
</a>
</div>
<!-- Audit -->
<div class="p-12 md:border-r border-outline-variant hover:bg-background transition-colors duration-500 group">
<div class="mb-12">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">balance</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-zl-headline-lg text-zl-headline-lg mb-6">Audit</h4>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
                            Transparent verification processes that provide absolute assurance. We look closer so you can see further.
                        </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-zen/contact">
                            Audit Clarity <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_right_alt</span>
</a>
</div>
<!-- Advisory -->
<div class="p-12 hover:bg-background transition-colors duration-500 group">
<div class="mb-12">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">self_improvement</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-zl-headline-lg text-zl-headline-lg mb-6">Advisory</h4>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
                            High-level strategic guidance for wealth preservation and growth. Merging traditional wisdom with modern foresight.
                        </p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm uppercase tracking-wider group-hover:underline" href="/templates/accounting-zen/contact">
                            Consult Wisdom <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_right_alt</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Visual Interlude -->
<section class="w-full h-[614px] relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-fixed bg-center" data-alt="A wide-angle, low-perspective view of minimalist Japanese architecture. Thin, dark wooden pillars frame a view of a serene courtyard where white gravel is raked into concentric circles around a single smooth river stone. The sky is a flat, pale grey, creating a soft, shadowless light that emphasizes the clean lines and geometric precision of the building. The image is strictly monochromatic, embodying quiet luxury and a calm, corporate aesthetic." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC5ooTRrEz0D2dq2lDOEIcCdn9CtxIgKcjf8XwS8QrTorrI9kU7oTGbc9dfNaHHLdi2lLNu_6EaioJfJW3y9d5z_PSCEYI3MkjwJdqA5TioNG1wJsk8N2Z3yhz3c-0PaBfY-gryepQXJmloSPMsY8btKwA0k4NavbpZ56rCA75SEUWw4kEyqc4yXz1SZ4CbJx75O1X55qCUeWKu-2gsQwccIHsBGJFm9RXf7JHcFV_IeVbIw1ffgDSbD0nYeBZgl0A9sujS3svIykLf')">
</div>
</section>
<!-- Dialogue CTA -->
<section class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-section-gap text-center" id="dialogue">
<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
<span class="font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8 block">Inquiry</span>
<h2 class="font-zl-display text-zl-display mb-8">Begin the Dialogue.</h2>
<p class="font-zl-body-lg text-zl-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-12">
                    Connect with our lead partners to discuss how we can bring precision and silence to your financial landscape.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap- gutter">
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-12 py-4 text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm border border-primary hover:bg-transparent hover:text-primary transition-all duration-300">
                        Schedule a Session
                    </button>
<button class="bg-transparent text-primary px-12 py-4 text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm border border-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-all duration-300">
                        Request a Prospectus
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
